PermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:665:\"<p>It&#8217;s always been possible to create blog posts and media-rich pages on WordPress, but it could have been easier. Now it is thanks to the WordPress Gutenberg editor. Without a doubt, Gutenberg transforms your editing experience in WordPress. Even if you&#8217;re an absolute newbie to WordPress, you can easily write articles and create media-rich pages. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gutenberg-blocks-plugins/\">14 Best WordPress Gutenberg Plugins to Enhance Your Editor (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19648:\"<p>It&#8217;s always been possible to create blog posts and media-rich pages on WordPress, but it could have been easier. Now it is thanks to the WordPress Gutenberg editor.</p>\n<p>Without a doubt, Gutenberg transforms your editing experience in WordPress. Even if you&#8217;re an absolute newbie to WordPress, you can easily write articles and create media-rich pages.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you some of the best WordPress Gutenberg plugins that enhance your editing experience.</p>\n<h3>Why You Need WordPress Gutenberg Plugins</h3>\n<p>WordPress comes with a lot of Gutenberg blocks, such as paragraph, image, bullet points, etc.  that let you easily build a page the way you want without having to memorize the shortcode. All you have to do is to choose the right block and add it to your page. If you want to enhance your editing experience even further, you can install a Gutenberg blocks plugin. </p>\n<p>For example, if you want to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Create a Contact Form on WordPress (the Easy Way)\">add a contact form to your page</a>, you just need to install WPForms and add the WPForms block from your Blocks list to your page. Best of all, instead of a shortcode, you&#8217;ll see the form fields in the editor, meaning you don&#8217;t have to switch to the preview page to see how your form would look like.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms, user registration,  plugin, user login plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231941\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is one of the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"17 Best Form Plugins for WordPress in 2019 (Most Are Free!)\">popular form builder plugins</a> that lets you create different kinds of forms using a block. Whether you want to add a contact form, survey form, payment form or any other forms, WPForms makes it easy to embed it onto your page. </p>\n<p>You can easily choose from its library of pre-built templates and start customizing it if you want. All forms you create with WPForms are responsive, meaning they look great on phone, tablet, and computer.  </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/envira-gallery-review.png\" alt=\"envira gallery review\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221521\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/envira-gallery-review.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/envira-gallery-review-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/envira-gallery-review-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Envira Gallery</a>, you can create image and video galleries on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">WordPress website</a>. You can use its native blocks to embed your galleries on your site.</p>\n<p>The plugin lets you use some really cool features on your galleries like watermark protection, image proofing etc. You can also sell your images with Easy Digital Downloads or WooCommerce integration. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomicblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. Atomic Blocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomicblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Aomic-blocks.png\" alt=\"Aomic blocks, gutenberg block plugins\" width=\"750\" height=\"329\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236376\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Aomic-blocks.png 750w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Aomic-blocks-300x132.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomicblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Atomic Blocks</a> is another amazing WordPress Gutenberg plugin that comes with great options to add beautiful custom blocks to your website. It&#8217;s a collection of blocks for the Gutenberg editor which let you easily build a page the way you want. </p>\n<p>It comes with a wide variety of blocks, such as advanced column block, newsletter block, pricing tables, containers, buttons and more. Best of all, you can use this plugin with any theme you want. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kadence-blocks-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. Kadence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kadence-blocks-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kadence-Blocks-Pro-Kadence-WP.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"469\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236378\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kadence-Blocks-Pro-Kadence-WP.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kadence-Blocks-Pro-Kadence-WP-300x182.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kadence-Blocks-Pro-Kadence-WP-768x465.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kadence-blocks-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Kadence</a> is an amazing WordPress Gutenberg block plugin that comes with beautiful custom blocks that are ready to use right away. Its block options run the gamut from icons, buttons to row and grid/carousel. </p>\n<p>All of these blocks are super flexible and supports 800+ Google fonts. You&#8217;ll also have over 1500 icons to choose from. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kingblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. KingBlocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kingblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kingblocks.png\" alt=\"Kingblocks\" width=\"775\" height=\"427\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236379\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kingblocks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kingblocks-300x165.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Kingblocks-768x423.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/kingblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >KingBlocks</a> is a WordPress Gutenberg plugin that comes with 20 striking blocks for your website. All blocks are fully responsive, so your content will look great regardless of the device you&#8217;re using to browse your site.</p>\n<p>KingBlocks makes use of the Leaflet JavaScript library to embed a mobile-friendly map on your pages. This plugin is compatible with most themes and plugins. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-cpelementia/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >6. CPElementia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-cpelementia/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/CPElementia.jpg\" alt=\"CPElementia\" width=\"775\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236380\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/CPElementia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/CPElementia-300x138.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/CPElementia-768x354.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-cpelementia/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >CPElementia</a> is yet another WordPress Gutenberg plugin that offers a huge collection of Gutenberg blocks and extended component features. This plugin is available to purchase from the Codecanyon marketplace.</p>\n<p>Here are a few blocks that are available on CPElementia: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>countdown timer </li>\n<li>feature boxes </li>\n<li>social icons</li>\n<li>pricing lists</li>\n<li>and more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-soloblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >7. Solo Blocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-soloblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Solo.png\" alt=\"Solo\" width=\"775\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236385\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Solo.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Solo-300x156.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Solo-768x400.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-soloblocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >SoloBlocks</a> is a nice plugin that let you create rich post layouts for your website. With this plugin, you can add additional blocks to your website without hassle. It offers the easiest way to add more blocks and you will just love it.</p>\n<p>This plugin is compatible with almost all modern themes and you can also use any other advanced plugin if you want alongside it. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-inster-instagram-block/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >8. Inster Instagram Block</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-inster-instagram-block/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Inster-–-Instagram-Block-for-WP.png\" alt=\"Gutenberg block plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"373\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236393\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Inster-–-Instagram-Block-for-WP.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Inster-–-Instagram-Block-for-WP-300x144.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Inster-–-Instagram-Block-for-WP-768x370.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Inster-–-Instagram-Block-for-WP-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The popularity of Instagram has been increasing every day. If you love using Instagram and want to showcase your profile on your WordPress website, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-inster-instagram-block/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Inster Instagram block</a> is one plugin that you need to check out. With this plugin, you can display your profile in a grid form using its Gutenberg blocks. </p>\n<p>Inster allows you to display Instagram feed using your username, location ID or tag. Your pictures will be shown great on all devices. It also lets you add initial animation effects to give you feed a distinct look. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/otter-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Otter Blocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/otter-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Otter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"258\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236394\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Otter.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Otter-300x100.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Otter-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/otter-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Otter</a> is a free Gutenberg block plugin that lets you add some really cool blocks to your website. You can use these blocks to create any kind of design including complex eCommerce pages. </p>\n<p>With Otter Blocks, you can add some advanced heading blocks, section blocks, button groups, testimonials, Google maps and more. It just takes you a few seconds to get it ready. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimate-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Ultimate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimate-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Ultimate.png\" alt=\"Ultimate block plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"258\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236395\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Ultimate.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Ultimate-300x100.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Ultimate-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimate-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Ultimate</a> is another popular WordPress Gutenberg plugin that have already bagged 2k active installs. This plugin provides you with a collection of 18 blocks to give a distinct look to your site.</p>\n<p>Whether you want to build a portfolio site, an eCommerce store or anything else, you have all the blocks you&#8217;ll need. Ultimate works beautifully with other advanced plugins and looks stunning on all screen sizes. It is also compatible across all browsers.  </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-gutenberg/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Advanced Gutenberg</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-gutenberg/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Advanced-Gutenberg.png\" alt=\"Advanced Gutenberg, block plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"271\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236396\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Advanced-Gutenberg.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Advanced-Gutenberg-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Advanced-Gutenberg-768x269.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-gutenberg/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Gutenberg</a> is an excellent plugin that comes with all the essential blocks you&#8217;ll need to enhance your editing experience. It comes with more than 20 brilliant blocks that are fully customizable. </p>\n<p>This is a free plugin that&#8217;s available to download from WordPress.org. It has been installed on over 10,000 websites all around the globe.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/stackable-ultimate-gutenberg-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">12. Stackable</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/stackable-ultimate-gutenberg-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Stackable-–-Gutenberg-Blocks.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"252\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236397\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Stackable-–-Gutenberg-Blocks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Stackable-–-Gutenberg-Blocks-300x98.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Stackable-–-Gutenberg-Blocks-768x250.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Use the ready-to-use custom blocks by <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/stackable-ultimate-gutenberg-blocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Stackable</a> to make your design stand out. All blocks offered by Stackable are super robust and extremely flexible. </p>\n<p>In total it offers 23 block styles. You can use these blocks to display your content beautifully. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/coblocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">13. Coblocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/coblocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/coblocks.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"255\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236404\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/coblocks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/coblocks-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/coblocks-768x253.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/coblocks/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Coblocks</a> is yet another Gutenberg block plugin that you need to check out. Although it&#8217;s a free plugin, it comes with the most amazing collection of blocks that you&#8217;ll love using. If you want a real page builder experience using the blocks, this is a plugin you will surely need.</p>\n<p>You will get to use more than 23 blocks to meet your requirements. From food block, gif blocks, click to tweet block and more, this plugin offers everything that is missing in the Gutenberg editor. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tinymce-advanced/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">14. TinyMCE</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tinymce-advanced/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/TinyMCE-Advanced-.png\" alt=\"TinyMCE Advanced\" width=\"775\" height=\"342\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236408\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/TinyMCE-Advanced-.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/TinyMCE-Advanced--300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/TinyMCE-Advanced--768x339.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tinymce-advanced/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">TinyMCE</a> is a bit different from the plugins that we discussed so far. This plugin helps you stick to your classic editor if you are still not ready to switch to Gutenberg. Plus, you can access all the amazing features of the block editor. </p>\n<p>The plugin comes with an improved “Clear Formatting” button, and several advanced settings for your tables. You also have an option to always keep paragraph tags in the block editor. </p>\n<p>These are some of the WordPress Gutenberg plugins that enhance your WordPress editing experience. If you want to <a ahref=\"https://optinmonster.com/11-web-design-principles-that-will-boost-your-conversion-rate/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">create beautiful websites that convert, here are some designing principles</a> you need to check out. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gutenberg-blocks-plugins/\">14 Best WordPress Gutenberg Plugins to Enhance Your Editor (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gutenberg-blocks-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";