ml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"google adsense alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"monetize your website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=232100\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:633:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Google AdSense alternatives to monetize your website? AdSense is the most popular advertising service in the world for earning money from ads. However, if your AdSense account is banned or deleted for any reason, then you&#8217;ll need to use another method to continue monetizing your content. In this article, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-google-adsense-alternatives/\">9 Best Google AdSense Alternatives to Monetize Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13095:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Google AdSense alternatives to monetize your website?</p>\n<p>AdSense is the most popular advertising service in the world for earning money from ads. However, if your AdSense account is banned or deleted for any reason, then you&#8217;ll need to use another method to continue monetizing your content.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best Google AdSense alternatives you can use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shareasale/\" title=\"ShareASale\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. ShareASale</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shareasale/\" title=\"ShareASale\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shareasale.jpg\" alt=\"ShareASale\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232111\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shareasale.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shareasale-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/shareasale-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ShareASale is the most popular affiliate marketing network. It offers multiple categories like fashion, technology, business, etc. which allows many varied business niches to earn extra money. You can sign up for any product that&#8217;s registered with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shareasale/\" title=\"ShareASale\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">ShareASale</a> and get your commission on each sale.</p>\n<p>It can be an alternative to Google AdSense as it generates income from your website traffic. It&#8217;s easy to join and you&#8217;ll be paid on a monthly basis. However, you&#8217;ll need the minimum $50 payment balance in your affiliate account to withdraw your revenue.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/media-net/\" title=\"Media.net\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Media.net</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/media-net/\" title=\"Media.net\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/medianet.jpg\" alt=\"Media.net\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232107\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/medianet.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/medianet-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/medianet-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Media.net is a similar service to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/google-adsense/\" title=\"Google AdSense\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Google AdSense</a> and can easily be used as an alternative. It displays contextual ads with customized designs that are relevant to your website&#8217;s content. It integrates with Yahoo! Bing Network&#8217;s contextual ads program to increase your outreach.</p>\n<p>With their native ads technique, they improve user engagement and personalize the look of your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">landing pages</a>. All their ads are fully responsive and look great on any screen size. Media.net pays out any revenue earned every 30 days.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://adbuff.com/\" title=\"AdBuff\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. AdBuff</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://adbuff.com/\" title=\"AdBuff\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adbuff.jpg\" alt=\"AdBuff\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232116\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adbuff.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adbuff-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adbuff-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>AdBuff is an AdSense-like ad network that connects you with advertisers. It has a real-time dashboard to see your revenue status, so you can properly manage your ads. The account manager allows you to review the performance of an ad and helps optimize it for better results.</p>\n<p>All their ads are family-friendly and protected from malicious content. It has integration with popular advertising companies to boost your revenue. AdBuff pays your earned revenue on a net 45 basis.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.bidvertiser.com/publisher/\" title=\"Bidvertiser\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Bidvertiser</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bidvertiser.com/publisher/\" title=\"Bidvertiser\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bidvertiser.jpg\" alt=\"Bidvertiser\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232115\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bidvertiser.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bidvertiser-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bidvertiser-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Bidvertiser is a direct advertising network you can use to monetize your website&#8217;s traffic and content. It has a control panel to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">optimize your traffic</a> and uses Smartlink technology to send your users directly to the chosen links. Unlike other ad services, your account will be approved right away. The ad formats include banners, sliders, popups, and more.</p>\n<p>It works with your website, mobile apps, extensions, and all other resources to monetize your traffic. Bidvertiser displays safe ads and integrates with popular payment services, like PayPal, to dispatch your revenue. You can withdraw your earned revenue with a balance as low as $10.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.popads.net/\" title=\"PopAds\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. PopAds</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.popads.net/\" title=\"PopAds\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/popads.jpg\" alt=\"PopAds\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232114\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/popads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/popads-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/popads-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>PopAds is a popular advertising network and ad publishing service. It&#8217;s a direct alternative to Google AdSense and is a high-paying solution. You can get your account approved and start publishing ads on your website in no time.</p>\n<p>All their ads are optimized to load quickly and efficiently. PopAds is liked by thousands of publishers for their unique payment criteria. They pay on a daily basis if you hit the minimum $5 / day target.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/\" title=\"Amazon Associates\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Amazon Associates</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/\" title=\"Amazon Associates\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/amazonassociates.jpg\" alt=\"Amazon Associates\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232113\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/amazonassociates.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/amazonassociates-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/amazonassociates-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Amazon Associates is one of the best affiliate programs in the world. It may not be a direct alternative to Google AdSense, but you can earn commissions from selling Amazon products on your website. If you own an <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">eCommerce store</a>, then you can simply sign up for the Amazon Associates program and display dynamic image ads on your website.</p>\n<p>Since Amazon has millions of products, you can choose to display the most relevant items to your product line. Amazon Associates pays up to 10% commission on each sale.</p>\n<p>You can also <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-amazon-affiliate-store-wordpress-make-money/\" title=\"How to Create an Amazon Affiliate Store With WordPress (and Make Money)\">create your own Amazon affiliate store</a> to earn more money.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://adsterra.com/\" title=\"Adsterra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Adsterra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://adsterra.com/\" title=\"Adsterra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adsterra.jpg\" alt=\"Adsterra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232112\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adsterra.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adsterra-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/adsterra-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Adsterra is a digital advertising network for publishers and advertisers. It comes with a personal account manager to monitor the performance of your ad campaigns. You can target web and mobile traffic separately to make the most of your ads. It also shows real-time performance statistics for your ads.</p>\n<p>All ads are secured by their in-house team and with the help of third-party solutions. The minimum payout for Adsterra is $100 and they pay twice a month to publishers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://publishers.propellerads.com/#/pub/auth\" title=\"Propeller Ads\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Propeller Ads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://publishers.propellerads.com/#/pub/auth\" title=\"Propeller Ads\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/propellerads.jpg\" alt=\"Propeller Ads\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232110\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/propellerads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/propellerads-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/propellerads-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Propeller Ads is another alternative to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/google-adsense/\" title=\"Google AdSense\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Google AdSense</a>. It&#8217;s a performance-driven advertising and affiliate network that allows you to create conversion-focused campaigns. It has an AI system that automates ad optimization and produces amazing results. Propeller Ads is a self-serving platform with real-time, in-depth statistics on your ads&#8217; performances.</p>\n<p>It offers multiple ad formats including onclick ads, native ads, etc. It also comes with an affiliate program to earn commissions on sales. You can choose from multiple payment gateways to pull out your income. Propeller Ads pay on a net 30 basis. For a few select countries, they also offer weekly payments.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.revenuehits.com/lps/pubref\" title=\"RevenueHits\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. RevenueHits</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.revenuehits.com/lps/pubref\" title=\"RevenueHits\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/revenuehits.jpg\" alt=\"RevenueHits\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232108\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/revenuehits.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/revenuehits-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/revenuehits-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>RevenueHits is another popular advertising network on the market. It guarantees quick approval of your account and boosts the ads to generate money from your website. It has multiple formats to display ads like banners, buttons, sliders, popups, etc.</p>\n<p>You can take out your revenue through PayPal, Payoneer, and other popular payment gateways. The minimum income amount to withdraw your money is $50, and they pay on a net 30 basis.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best Google AdSense alternatives to monetize your website. You may also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\" title=\"Top 10 Web Hosting Companies (Real Reviews, No B.S)\">best web hosting companies</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-google-adsense-alternatives/\">9 Best Google AdSense Alternatives to Monetize Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-google-adsense-alternatives/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";