0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"wordpress themes for book authors\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"wordpress themes for writers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=234387\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:620:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for book authors? A good WordPress theme makes it easy for writers to show off their portfolio and get more clients online. Book authors can use their website to sell books, connect with readers, and organize book signing events. In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-writers-authors/\">27 Best WordPress Themes for Writers and Book Authors (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37824:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for book authors?</p>\n<p>A good WordPress theme makes it easy for writers to show off their portfolio and get more clients online. Book authors can use their website to sell books, connect with readers, and organize book signing events.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress themes for writers and authors.</p>\n<h3>Choosing the Best WordPress Theme for Writers and Book Authors</h3>\n<p>To <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create a website</a> for writers and authors, you’ll need a WordPress theme that offers the right features that match your needs. You may know that there are thousands of WordPress themes for writers on the market, which makes it challenging to select the best theme for your website.</p>\n<p>Here are some of the key features you’ll often find on a WordPress theme for authors.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Modern and professional minimalistic layout</li>\n<li>Custom page templates for book description</li>\n<li>eCommerce support to sell books online</li>\n<li>Amazing typography to provide an excellent reading experience</li>\n<li>Showcase writing portfolio</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress themes for book authors and writers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi.jpg\" alt=\"Divi\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234395\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Divi</a> is a powerful WordPress theme and page builder. With Divi, you can create a website for book authors, writers, and bloggers. You can use the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">drag and drop page builder</a> to customize your website without editing any code. It also comes with several prebuilt demo websites to create pages quickly and easily.</p>\n<p>With its one-click demo install, you can quickly launch a writer / author website and create a distinct look by customizing your text and images. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-1.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234396\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">OceanWP</a> is a popular WordPress multi-purpose theme that lets you create any website, including one for writers. It offers demo websites for book authors, sellers, and writers. With its 1-click demo content installer, all you have to do is to import the demo site and then customize the content. </p>\n<p>This theme is built with SEO best practices in mind, so you can rest assured that you&#8217;ll be in good hands with OceanWP. OceanWP supports RTL languages, so you can translate your site to your preferred language with ease.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Astra Theme</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-1.jpg\" alt=\"Astra Theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234397\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Astra Theme</a> is a lightweight WordPress theme designed to build any website. It provides seamless integration with WordPress page builders so you can edit the layout the way you want with drag and drop. </p>\n<p>There are many ready-made starter sites, including a website for book authors, writers, and sellers. Astra Theme works great with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\" title=\"25 Must Have WordPress Plugins for Business Websites (Expert Pick)\">popular WordPress plugins</a> to extend the features and functionality.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-1.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234398\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Ultra</a> is a multi-purpose WordPress theme that allows you to create a website for book authors, publishers, and bloggers. It ships with dozens of theme skins to change the layout in 1-click. You can add unique features to your website using the free builder addons to give your site a unique look.</p>\n<p>Ultra is bundled with stunning features like smart layout options, color controls, parallax scrolling, mega menu, animations, and more. Ultra also comes with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-builder/\" title=\"Themify Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Themify Builder</a>, a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\">drag and drop page builder</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-author-pro/\" title=\"Author Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Author Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-author-pro/\" title=\"Author Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/author-pro.jpg\" alt=\"Author Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234399\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/author-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/author-pro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/author-pro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-author-pro/\" title=\"Author Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Author Pro</a> is an excellent WordPress theme built specifically for book authors, writers, sellers, online libraries, and publishing houses. It lets you showcase your books on the homepage along with a short description.</p>\n<p>This theme is powered by <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Framework</a>, which lays a solid foundation for your site. Like any other StudioPress theme, Author Pro also comes with several widgetized sections on the homepage, so you can set up your homepage by adding the right widgets.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-truenorth/\" title=\"True North\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. True North</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-truenorth/\" title=\"True North\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/truenorth.jpg\" alt=\"True North\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234400\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/truenorth.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/truenorth-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/truenorth-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-truenorth/\" title=\"True North\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">True North</a> is a free WordPress theme for book authors, writers, and publishers. It comes with several layout options, such as portfolio display, column listing, and isotope filtering. It comes with the portfolio content type to display your work on the homepage professionally.</p>\n<p>The theme offers custom widgets, and 1-click demo content installer. It seamlessly integrates with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WPML</a>, so you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">easily build a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/presence.jpg\" alt=\"Presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234401\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/presence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/presence-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/presence-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Presence</a> is a flexible WordPress theme designed to create a website for educational institutions, book authors, writers, and online libraries. Presence also comes with a drag and drop builder to get the look you want and import designs from their pre-built layouts.</p>\n<p>The Presence theme comes with 2 layouts (boxed and Full-width) and 10 website demos. Presence has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins for Engagement\">social media icons</a>, custom widgets, image sliders, and event calendar.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-hello-pro/\" title=\"Hello Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Hello Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-hello-pro/\" title=\"Hello Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hello-pro.jpg\" alt=\"Hello Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234402\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hello-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hello-pro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hello-pro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-hello-pro/\" title=\"Hello Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Hello Pro</a> is a simple WordPress theme built on top of Genesis framework. It lets you display a welcome message to your visitors and draw them into brand messaging. It includes custom page templates, homepage and footer widget areas, and a fully customizable header.</p>\n<p>Using the WordPress customizer, you can change colors, background, buttons, links, and fonts. This theme is highly optimized for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/boost-wordpress-performance-speed/\" title=\"How to Boost WordPress Performance &#038; Speed (Expert Advice)\">performance and speed</a>, so you can rest assured that your site doesn&#8217;t slow down because of the theme elements.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Hestia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hestiapro.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234403\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hestiapro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hestiapro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/hestiapro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Hestia</a> is a one-page WordPress multi-purpose theme for book authors, writers, publishers, and sellers. It offers a slick material design, which is perfect for building any type of websites.</p>\n<p>The theme has a customizable homepage with sections and blocks. You&#8217;ll get 2 extra options, a portfolio section and a fully customized Jetpack supported pricing section. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-neve/\" title=\"Neve\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Neve</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-neve/\" title=\"Neve\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/neve-1.jpg\" alt=\"Neve\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234404\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/neve-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/neve-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/neve-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-neve/\" title=\"Neve\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Neve</a> is a minimal WordPress theme with a sleek and simple design, which is perfect for creating a website for book authors, writers, and sellers. It comes with custom layout designs for the header and footer of your website.</p>\n<p>This theme is lightweight and built with blazing fast loading time in mind. You can customize most elements in this theme using WordPress customizer, so you don&#8217;t have to switch between preview and the editor.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Writee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/writee.jpg\" alt=\"Writee\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234405\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06