, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/modules-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/modules-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-modules/\" title=\"Modules\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Modules</a> is a delicate and sophisticated WordPress theme to create any website. It has a beautiful and flexible layout with fullscreen header background. This theme comes with multiple pre-built demo sites, including a template for book authors, writers, and publishers.</p>\n<p>It has a video background, color schemes, fonts, custom sidebars, and more. Modules theme supports WooCommerce and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" title=\"WPForms\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> plugins out of the box.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-pretty-creative/\" title=\"Pretty Creative\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">27. Pretty Creative</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-pretty-creative/\" title=\"Pretty Creative\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/pretty-creative.jpg\" alt=\"Pretty Creative\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234394\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/pretty-creative.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/pretty-creative-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/pretty-creative-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for an attractive and stylish WordPress theme for your website, then <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-pretty-creative/\" title=\"Pretty Creative\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Pretty Creative</a> is the right choice. It&#8217;s built on top of the Genesis theme framework that lays a strong foundation to the theme.</p>\n<p>The theme includes several custom page templates, widget areas, header layouts, color schemes, and theme options panel. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress themes for writesr and authors. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-apps/\" title=\"19 Best WordPress Themes for Mobile Apps &#038; Software\">best WordPress themes for mobile apps and software</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-writers-authors/\">27 Best WordPress Themes for Writers and Book Authors (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-writers-authors/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://www.isitwp.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{