:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"bluehost\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"best wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=549208\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:592:\"<p>So you&#8217;ve been looking at WordPress resume examples online and you&#8217;re ready to create your own. An online resume hosted on a WordPress website can make a powerful impression with a potential employer, build your online presence, network, and hopefully land you a great job. In this post, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best WordPress resume [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/\">25 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Land Your Dream Job</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42790:\"<p>So you&#8217;ve been looking at WordPress resume examples online and you&#8217;re ready to create your own.</p>\n<p>An online resume hosted on a WordPress website can make a powerful impression with a potential employer, build your online presence, network, and hopefully land you a great job.</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best WordPress resume themes out there so you can find one you love.</p>\n<h3>Getting Started with Your Online Resume Website</h3>\n<p>Before you pick your theme, you need to pick your <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/tips-and-tools-to-pick-the-best-domain-for-your-blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">domain name</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-hosting-guide\">WordPress hosting</a> in order to start a resume website on the platform.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s way simpler than it sounds, especially if you use <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Bluehost</a>. We recommend them to our readers because they are an official WordPress recommended host, affordable, and incredibly user-friendly.</p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to install WordPress. For a step-by-step tutorial on setting up Bluehost, WordPress, and installing the resume theme you pick, check out the guide <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/start-a-wordpress-blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How to Start a WordPress Blog</a>.</p>\n<p>But before you decide on a theme, it&#8217;s important to know what exactly to look for in a WordPress resume theme.</p>\n<h3>What to Look For in a WordPress Resume Theme</h3>\n<p>There are a ton of WordPress resume themes out there. Picking the one that works for you can be tricky if you aren&#8217;t sure which features you want and need.</p>\n<p>So, to make it easier on you, here are some key features of a fantastic resume theme:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Contact Info</strong> — Make sure potential employers have a way to reach you easily via email, social media, and a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-simple-contact-form-in-wordpress/\">contact form</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Professional-looking Design</strong> — You want your online resume to stand out from the crowd and appear well-designed, organized and non-distracting.</li>\n<li><strong>Mobile Friendly</strong> — Your theme should be responsive and look good on all devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Skills Section</strong> — You resume site needs an area where you can list the most important parts of your background like experience, skills, and education.</li>\n<li><strong>Portfolio Page</strong> — If you&#8217;re in a creative field or just need to showcase your past projects, a portfolio page with visuals of your work is a must.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Your resume theme doesn&#8217;t have to include all the above features, but now you have a good idea of what specifics to look for. Next, we&#8217;ll show you the best of the best in WordPress resume themes.</p>\n<h3>The Best WordPress Resume Themes</h3>\n<p>Here&#8217;s our hand-picked list of WordPress resume themes for all kinds of careers.</p>\n<h3>1. <a title=\"Astra WordPress Theme\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Astra</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Astra WordPress Theme\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549243\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/astra-theme-with-resume.png\" alt=\"astra theme with resume\" width=\"1116\" height=\"678\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/astra-theme-with-resume.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/astra-theme-with-resume-300x182.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/astra-theme-with-resume-768x467.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/astra-theme-with-resume-1024x622.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Astra WordPress Theme\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Astra</a> is a modern all-purpose theme that lets you build any kind of website, including a resume site. They offer tons of resume site templates and layouts for all types of careers.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Professional design with modern typography and gorgeous, mobile-responsive layouts</li>\n<li>Works with the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-drag-and-drop-wordpress-page-builders/\">most popular WordPress page builders</a></li>\n<li>Social media integration</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-woocommerce-plugins/\">WooCommerce</a>-ready</li>\n<li>Incredibly fast</li>\n<li>Includes support</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. To use the starter sites and layouts, you&#8217;ll need Astra Pro which costs $47/year or a one-time payment of $249.</p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549252\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/oceanwp-theme.png\" alt=\"oceanwp theme\" width=\"1116\" height=\"558\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/oceanwp-theme.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/oceanwp-theme-300x150.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/oceanwp-theme-768x384.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/oceanwp-theme-1024x512.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the most popular free WordPress themes around, <a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">OceanWP</a> is an excellence multipurpose theme to help you build a resume website.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/\">Multilanguage</a>-ready</li>\n<li>Easy 1-click layouts</li>\n<li>Works with page builders</li>\n<li>Lightning fast</li>\n<li>Very easy to use</li>\n<li>Can be used as a one page resume WordPress theme</li>\n<li>Modern full-screen display</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. You can buy their premium extensions individually or as a package for $39.</p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549293\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/divi-hello-child-theme.png\" alt=\"divi hello child theme\" width=\"1116\" height=\"703\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/divi-hello-child-theme.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/divi-hello-child-theme-300x189.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/divi-hello-child-theme-768x484.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/divi-hello-child-theme-1024x645.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Also at the top of our list is the multipurpose theme <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Divi</a>. To make an awesome-looking one page resume WordPress theme with Divi, you can use the Hello child theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Parallax scrolling for a cool animated effect</li>\n<li>Social follow buttons</li>\n<li>Sections for jobs, skills, education, awards, and more</li>\n<li>Resume download <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-the-perfect-call-to-action/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Call to Action (CTA) button</a></li>\n<li>Full-screen testimonial slider</li>\n<li>100s of beautifully designed layouts</li>\n<li>Includes support</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$89/year or a one-time payment of $249 will get you not only Divi, but access to 3 other themes by Elegant Themes.</p>\n<h3>4. <a title=\"ThemeIsle Hestia\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeisle-hestia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hestia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"ThemeIsle Hestia\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeisle-hestia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549259\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hestia-theme-by-themeisle.jpg\" alt=\"hestia theme by themeisle\" width=\"1116\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hestia-theme-by-themeisle.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-300x134.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-768x344.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-1024x459.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"ThemeIsle Hestia\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeisle-hestia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hestia</a>, a one page WordPress theme by ThemeIsle, is an excellent foundation for a slick and modern resume website.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerful and easy site customizer</li>\n<li>Page builder compatibility</li>\n<li>Portfolio section if you&#8217;d like to display your work</li>\n<li>Slider and video header</li>\n<li>Add a blog to attract employers via <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SEO</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$69.</p>\n<h3>5. <a title=\"Themify Ultra\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Themify Ultra\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549261\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ultra-theme-with-portfolio-layout.png\" alt=\"ultra theme with portfolio layout\" width=\"1116\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ultra-theme-with-portfolio-layout.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ultra-theme-with-portfolio-layout-300x188.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ultra-theme-with-portfolio-layout-768x482.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ultra-theme-with-portfolio-layout-1024x642.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Themify Ultra\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ultra</a> by Themify is another multi-purpose theme that offers a beautiful resume theme option when you use the Portfolio layout.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A built-in drag and drop page builder</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-themes/how-to-add-a-parallax-effect-to-any-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Parallax scrolling</a></li>\n<li>Mobile-responsive layouts</li>\n<li>Social media buttons</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$59.</p>\n<h3>6. <a title=\"Acme Themes Portfolio Web Pro\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/acme-themes-portfolio-web-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Portfolio Web Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Acme Themes Portfolio Web Pro\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/acme-themes-portfolio-web-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549302\" src=\"https://wpforms.com