el=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ShiftCV</a> is one of the best WordPress resume themes because it&#8217;s affordable, modest, and no-fuss.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sections for skills, experience and testimonial</li>\n<li>Options to print or download your resume directly from your site</li>\n<li>One page display with option blog page</li>\n<li>Dark or light color scheme</li>\n<li>Fully responsive</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$15.</p>\n<h3>19. <a title=\"Themeforest Deca\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-deca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Deca</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Themeforest Deca\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-deca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549644\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deca-.jpg\" alt=\"deca\" width=\"1116\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deca-.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deca--300x163.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deca--768x418.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deca--1024x558.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Themeforest Deca\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-deca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Deca</a> is a creative multi concept portfolio/CV template offered on ThemeForest. It&#8217;s one of the most affordable options on our list of the best WordPress resume themes.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Touch and swipe slider support</li>\n<li>Font Awesome integration for live icons</li>\n<li>Multiple portfolio, header, and homepage template styles</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$18.</p>\n<h3>20. <a title=\"Anariel Design Thinker\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">The Thinker</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Anariel Design Thinker\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549630\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/the-thinker.jpg\" alt=\"the thinker\" width=\"1116\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/the-thinker.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/the-thinker-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/the-thinker-768x465.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/the-thinker-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This fantastic resume theme by Anariel is called <a title=\"Anariel Design Thinker\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">The Thinker</a>. It&#8217;s perfect not only for online resumes, but for blogs and portfolios as well.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create your own layouts in the drag and drop builder</li>\n<li>WooCommerce support</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-responsive-contact-form-with-multiple-columns/\">Responsive</a> design</li>\n<li>Widgetized areas</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>A one-time payment of $59 gets you all 22+ of Anariel&#8217;s themes, including The Thinker.</p>\n<h3>21. <a title=\"Webnus Deep\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/webnus-deep/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Deep</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Webnus Deep\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/webnus-deep/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549626\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deep-theme-features-resume.jpg\" alt=\"deep theme features resume\" width=\"1116\" height=\"599\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deep-theme-features-resume.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deep-theme-features-resume-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deep-theme-features-resume-768x412.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/deep-theme-features-resume-1024x550.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The multipurpose <a title=\"Webnus Deep\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/webnus-deep/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Deep</a> theme features an amazing one page resume and CV layout that&#8217;s easy to set up and looks fantastic.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple page builder options</li>\n<li>Visual footer and header builders</li>\n<li>Dozens of included plugins for added features</li>\n<li>Responsive</li>\n<li>eCommerce available</li>\n<li>Download resume CTA button</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>A $49 one-time payment gets you access to all themes by the Deep theme creator, Webnus. Or, pay $89/year and get support, too.</p>\n<h3>22. <a title=\"Themeforest unRovr\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-unrovr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Unrovr</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Themeforest unRovr\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-unrovr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549624\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/creative-resume-cv-vcard-theme.jpg\" alt=\"creative resume, cv &amp; vcard theme\" width=\"1116\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/creative-resume-cv-vcard-theme.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/creative-resume-cv-vcard-theme-300x142.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/creative-resume-cv-vcard-theme-768x363.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/creative-resume-cv-vcard-theme-1024x484.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <a title=\"Themeforest unRovr\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themeforest-unrovr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Unrovr</a> theme is an animated vCard and resume builder WordPress theme used by 1,000s of people for their person and resume sites.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Drag and drop page builder</li>\n<li>Mobile-responsive</li>\n<li>Support responsive video embedding</li>\n<li>30+ social icons</li>\n<li>Gorgeous minimalist design</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>$49.</p>\n<h3>23. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Resumee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549622\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resumee-free-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"resumee free wordpress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"844\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resumee-free-wordpress.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resumee-free-wordpress-300x227.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resumee-free-wordpress-768x581.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resumee-free-wordpress-1024x774.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Resumee</a> is a wisely named free resume theme that offers a vCard template free that&#8217;s a good choice if you&#8217;re on a tight budget. It offers a straightforward design that&#8217;s distraction-free.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>100% responsive</li>\n<li>Full-screen layout</li>\n<li>Customizer with multiple options</li>\n<li>Simple one page theme perfect for professionals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free.</p>\n<h3>24. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/xtron/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Xtron</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/xtron/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-549604\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/one-page-resume-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"one page resume wordpress theme\" width=\"1116\" height=\"858\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/one-page-resume-wordpress-theme.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/one-page-resume-wordpress-theme-300x231.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/one-page-resume-wordpress-theme-768x590.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/one-page-resume-wordpress-theme-1024x787.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for free WordPress resume themes in 2019? <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/xtron/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Xtron</a> is a great pick since it doesn&#8217;t cost a cent and requires very little setup.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimalist design</li>\n<li>Slide-in navigation menu</li>\n<li>Compatible with page builder plugins</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<h3>25. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resume-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Resume Builder</a> (BONUS PLUGIN)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resume-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-549421 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resume-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"resume builder plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"630\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resume-builder-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resume-builder-plugin-300x169.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resume-builder-plugin-768x434.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/resume-builder-plugin-1024x578.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Although there&#8217;s no <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resume-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Resume Builder</a> WordPress theme, they do have an excellent plugin. It&#8217;s perfect if you already have a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-themes/\">WordPress theme</a> that you love and want to add your work history with an easy-to-use WordPress resume plugin.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Drag and drop resume builder</li>\n<li>Sections for skills, education, and experience</li>\n<li>Works with most WordPress themes</li>\n<li>Stunning default resume template</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free.</p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>There you have it! Hopefully, this post helped you find the best WordPress resume theme for your job search.</p>\n<p>And don&#8217;t forget to add WordPress skills on your resume since you built your resume website yourself, you rock star!</p>\n<p>Consider having employers reach you through your site&#8217;s contact form and check out our post on the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">best free form plugins for WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more updates from the blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/\">25 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Land Your Dream Job</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"Entry Management Just Got Better — Export Filters + Entries Dashboard\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://wpforms.com/entry-management-just-got-better/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://wpforms.com/entry-management-just-got-better/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 29 Aug 2019 12:00:50 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Announcement\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"form entries\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"form export\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"collect entries\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=548481\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:613:\"<p>Today we’re thrilled to announce that WPForms 1.5.5 has arrived. It’s now going to be simpler than ever to view and export form submissions from your site. You’ll be able to make better business decisions because you now have much more control over your form entries information. Here’s what’s happening in WPForms 1.5.5. Improved Entries [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/entry-management-just-got-better/\">Entry Management Just Got Better — Export Filters + Entries Dashboard</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5562:\"<p>Today we’re thrilled to announce that WPForms 1.5.5 has arrived.</p>\n<p>It’s now going to be simpler than ever to view and export form submissions from your site. You’ll be able to make better business decisions because you now have much more control over your form entries information.</p>\n<p>Here’s what’s happening in WPForms 1.5.5.</p>\n<h3>Improved Entries Exporting Experience</h3>\n<p>As WPForms has grown, so have our users. So many of you have become power users and have asked us for more control over exporting your form entries.</p>\n<p>Previously, the only way to export entries in WPForms was to go to the Entries area, click on view, and click on the Download Entries (CSV) button to save them all to your computer. And sometimes, that export wasn&#8217;t always reliable for those of you with tens of thousands of entries.</p>\n<p>There were also no filters and you would get all the entries from your forms — with no other options or report customizations.</p>\n<p>The new Entry Export feature can handle a massive amount of entries and lets you filter which ones you want to export. That way, you can save time finding the data you need inside your form submissions.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find the Export Entries feature under Tools » Export. It includes several filters for you to select or deselect based on the data you&#8217;d like on your exported CSV file including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Form Fields</li>\n<li>Additional Entry Information</li>\n<li>Date</li>\n<li>Search</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Want to quickly see the emails you&#8217;ve collected from a form but don&#8217;t want all the other info that was submitted? Use these checkboxes to customize which form fields will show up on your exported report to make things a little bit easier.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-548490\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/improved-entry-exporting.jpg\" alt=\"improved entry exporting\" width=\"1116\" height=\"692\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/improved-entry-exporting.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/improved-entry-exporting-300x186.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/improved-entry-exporting-768x476.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/improved-entry-exporting-1024x635.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>You can even add additional info, such as <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/geolocation-addon/\">Geolocation data</a> or <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/stripe-addon/\">Stripe payment</a> info if you&#8217;re using those addons. Plus, you’ll be able to search through your form fields to look for or exclude specific information.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-548492\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/additional-info.png\" alt=\"additional info\" width=\"1116\" height=\"786\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/additional-info.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/additional-info-300x211.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/additional-info-768x541.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/additional-info-1024x721.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>The Entry Exporting experience is much more polished and we think it&#8217;s going to make using WPForms even easier.</p>\n<h3>New Default Entries Page</h3>\n<p>Before, the Entries screen defaulted to the first form you made. Often, the first form you&#8217;ve ever created isn&#8217;t your most popular form. So, it wasn&#8217;t super useful to display that form as the default on this page.</p>\n<p>We wanted to make it simpler and faster to see your form entries. With this latest release, when you click on Entries you&#8217;ll now see an Entries Overview Dashboard with your forms&#8217; total entries instead.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-548505\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/entries-page.jpg\" alt=\"entries page\" width=\"1116\" height=\"795\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/entries-page.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/entries-page-300x214.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/entries-page-768x547.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/entries-page-1024x729.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll see all your forms on this new page, sorted by the amount of entries in the date range you select.</p>\n<p>You can also check out the All Time entries total and click on the Graph button to see <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/survey-data-visualization-tools/\">data visualization</a> of any of your forms. You&#8217;ll see a quick overview and be able to tell how your forms are performing with just a glance.</p>\n<p>And that covers it for the 2 new features you’ll find in WPForms 1.5.5. Try the latest version and keep us posted on what you think.</p>\n<p>As always, thank you for your continued support of WPForms. We look forward to helping you succeed with your website and business.</p>\n<p><em>Lisa and the WPForms team</em></p>\n<p>P.S. Don’t have a WPForms Pro license? <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/pricing\">Click here to get started today</a> and experience the WPForms difference.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/entry-management-just-got-better/\">Entry Management Just Got Better — Export Filters + Entries Dashboard</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://wpforms.com/entry-management-just-got-better/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"How to Create a Click To Call Button (the Easy Way) on WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://wpforms.com/create-a-click-to-call-button/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://wpforms.com/create-a-click-to-call-button/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 26 Aug 2019 12:00:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"mobile friendly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"wordpress.org\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"phone fields\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"small business\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"internet phone systems\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=542234\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:551:\"<p>Want to create a Click to Call button on your WordPress website? Since over 50% of web traffic happens on mobile devices, you want to make it easy for potential and current customers to call you with a simple click. In this tutorial, we&#8217;ll show you exactly how to add a Click to Call button [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/create-a-click-to-call-button/\">How to Create a Click To Call Button (the Easy Way) on WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16077:\"<p>Want to create a Click to Call button on your WordPress website?</p>\n<p>Since over 50% of web traffic happens on mobile devices, you want to make it easy for potential and current customers to call you with a simple click.</p>\n<p>In this tutorial, we&#8217;ll show you exactly how to add a Click to Call button to your WordPress site.</p>\n<h3>Why Add a Click to Call Link?</h3>\n<p>It&#8217;s very important as a small business owner to collect as high-quality leads as possible.</p>\n<p>Not everyone wants to give you their <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-setup-a-free-business-email-address/\">email address</a> or telephone numbers, but they still might want to do business with you.</p>\n<p>Give them a chance to do it by letting them call you — and to make it as easy as possible, add a clickable phone number button.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542382\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-now-button-desktop-users-or-mobile-devices.jpg\" alt=\"call now button desktop users or mobile devices\" width=\"558\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-now-button-desktop-users-or-mobile-devices.jpg 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-now-button-desktop-users-or-mobile-devices-300x162.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>Since more and more people are using their mobile device to search the web, users sometimes want to speak with a person right away on the same device.</p>\n<p>Luckily there&#8217;s a <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">clickable phone numbers button plugin called WP Call Button</a> that does this for you without you having to know any html code. You don&#8217;t have to be very technical to use it.</p>\n<p>Next, let&#8217;s take a look at how to add a Click to Call Now Button on WordPress using this plugin.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Add a Click to Call Button in WordPress</h3>\n<p>Asking yourself how do I make a phone number button clickable in WordPress? It&#8217;s super easy with the (free) WP Call Button plugin. Just follow these steps:</p>\n<h3>Step 1. Install the Free WP Call Button Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Click here to download the WP Call Button</a> from WordPress.org.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542356\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-a-click-to-call-button-to-your-wordpress-site-in-minutes.jpg\" alt=\"add a click to call button to your wordpress site in minutes\" width=\"1116\" height=\"529\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-a-click-to-call-button-to-your-wordpress-site-in-minutes.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-a-click-to-call-button-to-your-wordpress-site-in-minutes-300x142.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-a-click-to-call-button-to-your-wordpress-site-in-minutes-768x364.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-a-click-to-call-button-to-your-wordpress-site-in-minutes-1024x485.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>For detailed instructions, check out <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to install a WordPress plugin for beginners</a>.</p>\n<h3>Step 2. Locate the WP Call Button Plugin Settings</h3>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve activated the plugin on your WordPress site, you&#8217;ll want to configure the settings to your liking.</p>\n<p>To find the WP Call Button settings area, go to the left-hand panel of your WordPress dashboard and click on <strong>Settings</strong> » <strong>WP Call Button</strong>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542340\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/how-to-configure-wp-call-button-settings.jpg\" alt=\"how to configure wp call button settings\" width=\"1116\" height=\"772\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/how-to-configure-wp-call-button-settings.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/how-to-configure-wp-call-button-settings-300x208.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/how-to-configure-wp-call-button-settings-768x531.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/how-to-configure-wp-call-button-settings-1024x708.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>This settings page will open on the Sticky Call Button page. This type of button appears on the bottom of the user&#8217;s screen and moves up and down as they scroll, so it&#8217;s always visible. It&#8217;s also the most popular type of Click to Call buttons because it converts extremely well.</p>\n<h3>Step 3. Enter Your Business Phone Number</h3>\n<p>Now, enter your <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\">business telephone number</a> where you want to receive the phone calls coming from your website visitors.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542498\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/phone-number-area.png\" alt=\"phone number area\" width=\"1116\" height=\"192\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/phone-number-area.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/phone-number-area-300x52.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/phone-number-area-768x132.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/phone-number-area-1024x176.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>The WP Call Button plugin uses the smart phone number field which means you can pick your country and it will automatically add the country code in the proper format.</p>\n<p>If you don’t have a business phone number, then you can get one from <a title=\"Nextiva\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Nextiva</a>. You can control how you forward the calls to places including mobile phones instead of just landlines.</p>\n<h3>Step 4. Edit the Button Text</h3>\n<p>Next, you can change the call button text to say whatever you like. Simply click inside the text box where the default message &#8220;Call Us&#8221; is and edit it.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542553\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-call-button-text.png\" alt=\"edit call button text\" width=\"1116\" height=\"162\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-call-button-text.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-call-button-text-300x44.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-call-button-text-768x111.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-call-button-text-1024x149.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Editing the Click to Call button text will only work if you have a button in a Full-width position (it&#8217;s the only one that displays text). We&#8217;ll talk about button positions in the next step.</p>\n<h3>Step 5. Pick the Button Position</h3>\n<p>Now, decide which call button position works best for your website. There are 4 choices. However, <strong>full-width buttons</strong> receive the most conversions and will be the most effective to get you more online leads.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542559\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-button-position.jpg\" alt=\"select button position\" width=\"1116\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-button-position.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-button-position-300x85.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-button-position-768x217.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-button-position-1024x289.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 6. Edit the Button Color</h3>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll want to edit the color of the phone call link button. Try using one of your business&#8217; brand colors or a color that matches your <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-small-business/\">small business WordPress theme</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542567\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/change-button-color.jpg\" alt=\"change button color\" width=\"1116\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/change-button-color.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/change-button-color-300x48.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/change-button-color-768x124.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/change-button-color-1024x165.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 7. Pick the Call Button Visibility</h3>\n<p>Decide where you want your call button to be shown. It&#8217;s popular to display it everywhere on your site, so that&#8217;s the default. But you can also show it and/or hide it on only certain pages or posts.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542569\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-button-visibility.jpg\" alt=\"call button visibility\" width=\"1116\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-button-visibility.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-button-visibility-300x73.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-button-visibility-768x187.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/call-button-visibility-1024x250.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 8. Save Changes</h3>\n<p>Click on the green Save Changes button on the bottom left of the settings page once everything in the settings is configured to your liking.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542572\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-the-save-changes-button.jpg\" alt=\"select the save changes button\" width=\"1116\" height=\"571\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-the-save-changes-button.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-the-save-changes-button-300x153.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-the-save-changes-button-768x393.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/select-the-save-changes-button-1024x524.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 9. Turn Your Button on</h3>\n<p>When you&#8217;ve successfully configured all the WP Call Button settings the way you want them, scroll to the top of the page and click on the green toggle icon to turn your Click to Call button on.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542583\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/display-call-now-button-on.jpg\" alt=\"display call now button on\" width=\"1116\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/display-call-now-button-on.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/display-call-now-button-on-300x153.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/display-call-now-button-on-768x392.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/display-call-now-button-on-1024x522.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you can visit your site and see the call button in action.</p>\n<h3>Step 10: Set Up a Static Click to Call Button (Optional)</h3>\n<p>You also have the option to add a static call button in your WordPress contact page, about page, or any other post/page on your site.</p>\n<p>A static Click to Call button will stay in place even when the user scrolls away, so it&#8217;s not always visible.</p>\n<p>To add your static Click to Call button, create a new page or post in WordPress and click on the plus icon. Here, you&#8217;ll select the <strong>WP Call Button</strong> block.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542517\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-wp-call-button-to-site-static.jpg\" alt=\"add wp call button to site static\" width=\"1116\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-wp-call-button-to-site-static.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-wp-call-button-to-site-static-300x164.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-wp-call-button-to-site-static-768x420.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-wp-call-button-to-site-static-1024x560.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Inside the block editor on the right, you can change the font size, plus the color of the static button background and text.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542601\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-your-call-button-block.jpg\" alt=\"edit your call button block\" width=\"1116\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-your-call-button-block.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-your-call-button-block-300x194.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-your-call-button-block-768x495.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/edit-your-call-button-block-1024x661.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, select the blue <strong>Publish</strong> button in the top right corner to make your page or post live. Then, the static button will be displayed on your site.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-542603\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-call-us-button-to-wordpress-website.jpg\" alt=\"add call us button to wordpress website\" width=\"1116\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-call-us-button-to-wordpress-website.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-call-us-button-to-wordpress-website-300x116.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-call-us-button-to-wordpress-website-768x298.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/add-call-us-button-to-wordpress-website-1024x397.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>After reading this, you can probably see why we recommend WP Call Button to add a call us now button to your website. It&#8217;s definitely the easiest and most powerful WordPress Click to Call button plugin on the market.</p>\n<p>And the coolest part of this awesome plugin is that it’s 100% free.</p>\n<p>Plus, it works with <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-google-analytics-plugins-for-wordpress/\">Google Analytics</a> if you&#8217;re using the <a href=\"http://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin. It automatically tracks how many people click on your Click to Call button, so you can sit back and focus on <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/make-money-online/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">making more money online</a>.</p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>And there you have it! We hope this tutorial helped you add a Click to Call button, to your WordPress site easily.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our post on the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems\">best internet phone systems and VoIP for small business</a>.</p>\n<p>And if you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more WordPress tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/create-a-click-to-call-button/\">How to Create a Click To Call Button (the Easy Way) on WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i