lax scrolling for animated effects</li>\n<li>A live preview to see your work while you change it on the frontend</li>\n<li>A basic or advanced theme customizer to support the needs of beginners and developers</li>\n<li>Fantastic documentation and support for help when you need it</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And every single one of Themify’s WordPress themes are <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/glossary/responsive-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">100% responsive</a> and mobile-friendly, so they&#8217;ll look awesome on any device.</p>\n<p>But the coolest part about Themify? If you can&#8217;t decide on a theme, you can <a title=\"Themify\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">join their Theme Club</a> and access them all — saving yourself a lot of money.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a site that lets even beginners customize their websites exactly the way they want it, Themify could be a fantastic choice for you.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;re delighted to work with <a title=\"Themify\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Themify</a> to keep creating user-friendly tools that make it effortless to build your own professional-looking website.</p>\n<p>Not using WPForms yet? <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\">Click here to get started with WPForms today</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-themify-build-amazing-customized-sites-in-minutes/\">WPForms + Themify: Build Amazing Customized Sites in Minutes</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-themify-build-amazing-customized-sites-in-minutes/feed/\";s:7:\"att