s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=530230\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:624:\"<p>Looking for other options besides Rafflecopter to create a free online giveaway? Organizing a giveaway is a great way to skyrocket your online growth, and there are even free tools to help you. In this post, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best Rafflecopter alternatives and their coolest features. The Best Rafflecopter Alternatives To create a successful [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/rafflecopter-alternatives-create-free-giveaway/\">9 Best Rafflecopter Alternatives to Create a Free Giveaway (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26226:\"<p>Looking for other options besides Rafflecopter to create a free online giveaway?</p>\n<p>Organizing a giveaway is a great way to skyrocket your online growth, and there are even free tools to help you.</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best Rafflecopter alternatives and their coolest features.</p>\n<h3 id=\"rafflecopteralternatives\">The Best Rafflecopter Alternatives</h3>\n<p>To create a successful free online giveaway, you should check out these Rafflecopter alternatives:</p>\n<h3>1. <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RafflePress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-517123 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress.jpg\" alt=\"best wordpress podcasting plugins rafflepress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-300x127.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-768x326.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-1024x434.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\">RafflePress</a> is the FREE must-have giveaway plugin for a killer marketing strategy. It really is the best WordPress giveaway plugin that lets you create a giveaway free. Not only that, but the free version has a ton of amazing features you can use without spending a cent.</p>\n<p><strong>Free Version Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy-to-use drag and drop sweepstakes builder with access to everything needed to create a successful giveaway in minutes</li>\n<li>100% mobile responsive</li>\n<li>Fraud protection helps keep your contest fair</li>\n<li>Rule generator template</li>\n<li>Highly optimized giveaway widgets are lightning fast to help with site speed, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SEO</a> and conversion rates</li>\n<li>Automated contest start and end times</li>\n<li>A free giveaway template</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-530938\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rafflepress-free-giveaway-template.jpg\" alt=\"rafflepress free giveaway template\" width=\"1116\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rafflepress-free-giveaway-template.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rafflepress-free-giveaway-template-300x210.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rafflepress-free-giveaway-template-768x537.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rafflepress-free-giveaway-template-1024x717.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>On top of the ability to create a sweepstakes free, RafflePress has some amazing features you can get with the Pro version.</p>\n<p><strong>Pro Version Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tons of email marketing integrations to help you connect your email list and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/get-more-email-subscribers/\">get more subscribers</a></li>\n<li>Custom backgrounds and design options</li>\n<li>Giveaway competition landing page</li>\n<li>Goal-based giveaway templates</li>\n<li>Viral sharing features gets you more traffic by rewarding users with bonus entries for referring friends to your giveaway and sharing it on their social media</li>\n<li>Verified bonus actions let users earn more entries by following you on social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, Pinterest, Twitter, and more</li>\n</ul>\n<p>RaffePress gets your website visitors to bring you more website visitors, and they get the chance to win something, so everyone benefits. You can check out <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/rafflepress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RafflePress reviews</a> yourself and read why smart business owners are loving this free online contest software.</p>\n<p><strong>RafflePress Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>RafflePress has an amazing <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rafflepress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">free version</a>. The Pro version starts at $39.20/year.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Click here to get the world&#8217;s best WordPress giveaway plugin, RafflePress, today</a>!</p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"Wishpond\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/wishpond/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Wishpond</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Wishpond\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/wishpond/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-530269 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/wishpond-marketing-strategy-with-giveaways.jpg\" alt=\"wishpond marketing strategy with giveaways\" width=\"1116\" height=\"443\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/wishpond-marketing-strategy-with-giveaways.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/wishpond-marketing-strategy-with-giveaways-300x119.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/wishpond-marketing-strategy-with-giveaways-768x305.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/wishpond-marketing-strategy-with-giveaways-1024x406.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Much more than a giveaway platform, <a title=\"Wishpond\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/wishpond/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Wishpond</a> is a marketing platform that can handle tons of different online marketing needs. Although it may be too big of a platform for those looking for a simple WordPress giveaway plugin, we&#8217;ll look at their contest and promotions product below.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple and modern user interface to build awesome giveaway campaigns and social promotions</li>\n<li>Offers 300+ integrations with email marketing platforms, CRMs, payment processors, and more</li>\n<li>Has 10 social media competitions and contests including Instagram hashtag contests, photo caption contests, video contests, and more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Wishpond Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Starts at $49/month (billed annually) — Create a free online giveaway during your 14-day free trial.</p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"WooRise\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/woorise/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Woorise</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"WooRise\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/woorise/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-530257\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woorise-giveaways-and-contests-social-promotions.jpg\" alt=\"woorise giveaways and contests social promotions\" width=\"1116\" height=\"487\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woorise-giveaways-and-contests-social-promotions.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woorise-giveaways-and-contests-social-promotions-300x131.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woorise-giveaways-and-contests-social-promotions-768x335.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woorise-giveaways-and-contests-social-promotions-1024x447.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <a title=\"WooRise\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/woorise/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Woorise</a> online giveaway plugin lets you create an online contest for free. Some of the cooler features are limited to paid plans.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/conditional-logic/\">Conditional logic</a> to customize the user experience</li>\n<li>Fraud detection and 1-click random winners</li>\n<li>Create your free online raffle to be shared with social action buttons including Facebook Like, Instagram Follow, Twitter Follow, YouTube Subscribe, and more</li>\n<li>Pre-made layouts and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/\">multilingual</a> support</li>\n<li>Premium Grow version includes priority email and chat support</li>\n<li>Email integrations with the Grow version</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong> Woorise Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. Premium Grow version pricing starts at around $55/month.</p>\n<h3>4. <a title=\"Agorapulse Timeline Contest\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/agorapulse-timeline-contest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Agorapulse</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Agorapulse Timeline Contest\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/agorapulse-timeline-contest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-530281\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/agorapulse-social-media-marketing-strategy.png\" alt=\"agorapulse social media marketing strategy\" width=\"1116\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/agorapulse-social-media-marketing-strategy.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/agorapulse-social-media-marketing-strategy-300x129.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/agorapulse-social-media-marketing-strategy-768x330.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/agorapulse-social-media-marketing-strategy-1024x440.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Agorapulse Timeline Contest\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/agorapulse-timeline-contest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Agorapulse</a> is a complete social media management platform, and the pricing reflects that. However, you&#8217;ll get access to their Facebook contest feature, which is awesome. So, if you&#8217;re in the market for both a social media manager tool and a Facebook giveaway service, this would make a decent pick.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sweepstakes for people who have liked and/or commented on a post</li>\n<li>Quizzes help you engage fans then randomly pick a winner from the comments with the correct answers</li>\n<li>Photo contests</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Could you follow Facebook&#8217;s guidelines and run a timeline contest yourself? Sure. But filtering the likes and comments manually could take hours of work.</p>\n<p><strong>Agorapulse Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Starts at $89/month (billed annually) — Create a free online giveaway during your 30 day free trial (Their 15 day trial is renewable once).</p>\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://www.easypromosapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Easypromos</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.easypromosapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-530287 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Easypromos-instagram-contests.png\" alt=\"Easypromos review instagram contests\" width=\"1116\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Easypromos-instagram-contests.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Easypromos-instagram-contests-300x138.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Easypromos-instagram-contests-768x352.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Easypromos-instagram-contests-1024x470.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easypromos is a platform to create and manage digital promotions across all social networks. And our <a href=\"https://www.easypromosapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Easypromos</a> review is favorable, especially since it&#8217;s so easy to use.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Exclusive contests combining Facebook, Twitter and Instagram</li>\n<li>Use marketing products like surveys and polls</li>\n<li>Easypromos Instagram Giveaway Tool creates a contest among the entrants who comment on your Instagram post, and generates a random winner</li>\n<li>100% responsive and mobile-friendly</li>\n<li>Can be used on WordPress with a widget</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Easypromos Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Starts at around $25/month (billed annually) — You can create 1 free online giveaway.</p>\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://www.shortstack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ShortStack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.shortstack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-530245\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/shortstack-giveaway-website.jpg\" alt=\"shortstack giveaway website\" width=\"1116\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/shortstack-giveaway-website.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/shortstack-giveaway-website-300x193.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/shortstack-giveaway-website-768x493.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/shortstack-giveaway-website-1024x658.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the more popular Rafflecopter alternatives on our list, <a href=\"https://www.shortstack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ShortStack</a> answers the &#8216;how do you start a giveaway&#8217; question by making giveaway campaigns so easy to create you can do it in minutes. It&#8217;s a robust digital marketing platform built for engagement, marketing automation, and of course, lead collection.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>20+ widgets including form, poll, newsletter, social media, gallery and voting</li>\n<li>Simple drag and drop builder</li>\n<li>Customized design options with size, text, color, and more</li>\n<li>Email campaign entrants automatically through ShortStack</li>\n<li>Collects leads in a searchable database with no storage limits</li>\n<li>Restricts repeated entries and verifies authenticity to reduce contest fraud and improve the quality of your email list</li>\n<li>The Random Entry Selector works for all types of contests on social networks, including as a Facebook contest winner generator</li>\n<li>Use Shortstack as a photo contest platform with their hashtags based photo contests</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>ShortStack Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. Premium version starts at $29/month.</p>\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://kingsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">KingSumo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://kingsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-530286\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/kingsumo-online-giveaways-rafflecopter-alternative.jpg\" alt=\"kingsumo online giveaways rafflecopter alternative\" width=\"1116\" height=\"594\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/kingsumo-online-giveaways-rafflecopter-alternative.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/kingsumo-online-giveaways-rafflecopter-alternative-300x160.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/kingsumo-online-giveaways-rafflecopter-alternative-768x409.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/kingsumo-online-giveaways-rafflecopter-alternative-1024x545.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://kingsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">KingSumo</a> helps you grow your email list through online giveaways. They created the software for their own company, AppSumo, and it worked so well they decided to share the technology.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>This online contest software lets you set up your giveaway on your WordPress site in just a few clicks</li>\n<li>Schedule start and end dates ahead of time</li>\n<li>Easy image uploads to show a picture of the prize next to its description</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>KingSumo Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. The WordPress plugin license costs $198</p>\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gleam/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gleam</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gleam/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-530278 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gleam-giveaway-site.png\" alt=\"giveaway site is gleam free\" width=\"1116\" height=\"486\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gleam-giveaway-site.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gleam-giveaway-site-300x131.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gleam-giveaway-site-768x334.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gleam-giveaway-site-1024x446.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Although it&#8217;s the most expensive of the Rafflecopter alternatives on our list, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gleam/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gleam</a>&#8216;s sweepstakes maker makes it super easy to host an online giveaway through your social networks.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-google-analytics-plugins-for-wordpress/\">Google Analytics</a> integration</li>\n<li>Verified actions check the entries to social networks actually went through</li>\n<li>Reach more people by letting users refer friends with custom referral links</li>\n<li>Responsive widgets for a mobile-friendly user experience</li>\n<li>Random selection to make picking your winner a breeze</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Although it&#8217;s got a lot of great features, it&#8217;s a lot of money for all those functions. And some of the Gleam competitors out there have been really stepping up their game and becoming more popular for good reason.</p>\n<p><strong>Gleam Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. While Gleam offers a premium $10/month Hobby plan that&#8217;s pretty limited, the Business plan starts at $149/month.</p>\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woobox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Woobox</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woobox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-530289 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woobox-giveaway-campaigns.jpg\" alt=\"woobox giveaway campaigns giveaway on youtube\" width=\"1116\" height=\"612\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woobox-giveaway-campaigns.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woobox-giveaway-campaigns-300x165.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woobox-giveaway-campaigns-768x421.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/woobox-giveaway-campaigns-1024x562.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The free online contest software <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woobox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Woobox</a> lets you set up your giveaway on your WordPress site in just a few clicks. Create a contest online free with this beautifully designed marketing platform.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The software has an additional plugin you can install to embed your giveaway campaigns on your WordPress site with shortcodes</li>\n<li>The free giveaway template lets you easily customize and in just a few clicks create a sweepstakes free</li>\n<li>Offers landing pages to drive traffic from emails, social media posts, and ads to a dedicated page</li>\n<li>Collect entries from hashtags, likes, and comments on social sites</li>\n<li>Has a variety of campaigns like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\">polls</a>, giveaways, contests and instant wins</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Woobox Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. The premium versions start at $32/month</p>\n<h3>The Best Rafflecopter Alternatives Winner</h3>\n<p>Our pick for the best Rafflecopter alternatives winner is <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RafflePress</a>. Here&#8217;s why:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Completely dedicated to giveaways, not just an addon of a bigger software with tons of unrelated features</li>\n<li>It&#8217;s free and much more affordable than the others on this list to get the premium version at around $39/year</li>\n<li>It&#8217;s insanely easy to use and even beginners can create giveaways and add them to their WordPress websites</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So what are you waiting for? Get started with the <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">premium version of RafflePress</a>, or grab the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rafflepress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">completely free version of RafflePress</a> today.</p>\n<p>So now that you know the best Rafflecopter alternatives, you might want to learn more about online giveaways by reading our in-depth FAQ next.</p>\n<h3>FAQs</h3>\n<p>We get a lot of questions about free WordPress giveaway plugins, so we&#8217;ve put together a handy FAQ here.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Run a Contest Online?</h3>\n<p>The easiest, most effective, and most popular way to run a social contest for your online business is by <strong>hosting giveaways</strong>. Wondering how to run a giveaway? First, make sure you understand what a giveaway actually is and means.</p>\n<h3>What Are Giveaways?</h3>\n<p>Online giveaways are promotional drawings (sweepstakes, technically) where a prize is given away to a participant chosen at random from a pool of entries.</p>\n<h3>What Are the Best Giveaways?</h3>\n<p>Whether your digital marketing strategy includes growing your email list or simply getting more followers, the best online giveaways are usually <strong>social media contests</strong>. This just simply means that your contest is easily shareable via social media.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Make sure to check out this guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-successful-giveaway-wordpress-site/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to create a successful giveaway on your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<h3>How Do I Track and Manage a Social Media Contest?</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;re using a WordPress website for your business online, the simplest way to track and manage social media contests on your social networks is with a WordPress giveaway plugin like <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RafflePress</a>. With a social promotions tool like a giveaway plugin, you can track and manage your social media contests through an easy-to-use software.</p>\n<h3>How Do You Pick a Winner for a Giveaway?</h3>\n<p>You can use RafflePress to pick your winner with the random generator.</p>\n<p>But, before you pick your winner, make sure you&#8217;ve let your email list know about your giveaway. You can do this easily with RafflePress, since they have tons of <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">email marketing</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/top-crms-for-your-small-business/\">CRM</a> integrations. Also, spread the word about your social media giveaway by submitting your contest to <a href=\"https://woorise.com/promote-giveaway-contest-free)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">free giveaway websites</a>.</p>\n<h3>Are Giveaways Allowed on Instagram?</h3>\n<p>Wondering to yourself can you promote a giveaway on Instagram? Great news, you can absolutely promote a giveaway on your Instagram account. Just make sure you are closely following <a href=\"https://help.instagram.com/179379842258600\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Instagram&#8217;s official Promotion Guidelines</a>.</p>\n<h3>How Can I Do a Free Giveaway on Instagram?</h3>\n<p>Yes, you can do a free giveaway on Instagram. If you&#8217;re using a free tool like the Rafflecopter alternatives listed above, you can share your contest via Instagram from the tool.</p>\n<p>The easiest way to keep track of an Instagram Giveaway is to use one of <a href=\"#rafflecopteralternatives\">these tools</a>.</p>\n<h3>Are Facebook Giveaways Legal?</h3>\n<p>You may be asking yourself is it illegal to do giveaways on Facebook? And the answer is, it depends.</p>\n<p>It all depends on the terms of the giveaway, where you live, how you conduct it, and type of social promotions you run on the social media network.</p>\n<p>Keep yourself super aware of these rules. If you&#8217;re in the U.S., check out this great post about <a href=\"https://www.semrush.com/blog/facebook-promotions-us-law-contests/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook contests and sweepstakes</a>.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Create a Giveaway on Facebook?</h3>\n<p>You can get started creating a free giveaway to share on Facebook by installing and setting up <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RafflePress</a> today.</p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>And there you have it. Hopefully, this post helped you find a Rafflecopter alternative to create a free online giveaway that works for you and your site&#8217;s needs.</p>\n<p>Plus, we hope we&#8217;ve helped answer your questions and you&#8217;ve learned how to create a giveaway.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re about to launch a site or a new page, you should definitely read our post about the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-coming-soon-plugins-and-themes/\">best WordPress coming soon plugins and themes</a>.</p>\n<p>And don’t forget, if you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/rafflecopter-alternatives-create-free-giveaway/\">9 Best Rafflecopter Alternatives to Create a Free Giveaway (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://wpforms.com/rafflecopter-alternatives-create-free-giveaway/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"Lead Generation Forms: 23 Examples That Convert (Like Crazy)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://wpforms.com/lead-generation-forms-examples/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://wpforms.com/lead-generation-forms-examples/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 07 Aug 2019 12:00:59 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"multi-page form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"OptinMonster\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"lead magnet\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=524352\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:584:\"<p>Want some design inspiration to get more conversions on your site? Your forms can convert like crazy if you follow the psychological and design tactics that the forms on this list do. In this post, we&#8217;ve searched the web and found some excellent lead generation forms examples to help increase your form conversion rates. What [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/lead-generation-forms-examples/\">Lead Generation Forms: 23 Examples That Convert (Like Crazy)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31765:\"<p>Want some design inspiration to get more conversions on your site?</p>\n<p>Your forms can convert like crazy if you follow the psychological and design tactics that the forms on this list do.</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ve searched the web and found some excellent lead generation forms examples to help increase your form conversion rates.</p>\n<h3>What Is a Lead Generation Form?</h3>\n<p>A lead generation form is a web form meant for capturing emails and other information of potential customers. The most common types of lead generation forms include contact forms, registration forms, and simple newsletter signup forms.</p>\n<h3>How Do You Optimize Lead Generation?</h3>\n<p>You&#8217;ll see a few themes of effective tactics on this list of lead generation forms examples.</p>\n<p>Many of these examples use a combination of some of these simple form optimization tricks:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use a compelling call to action button</li>\n<li>Offer a discount</li>\n<li>Optimize your pre-existing content as a lead magnet</li>\n<li>Create distraction-free landing pages</li>\n<li>Make multi-step forms if you have a long form</li>\n<li>Try gamified <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-discount-wheel-popup-plugins/\">discount wheel popups</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some examples of how brands are using these and other lead generation forms tricks next.</p>\n<h3>Lead Generation Form Examples</h3>\n<p>To help you navigate the different niches of businesses online, here&#8217;s a list of the brands on our list of lead generation form examples.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#backtotheroots\">Back to the Roots</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#chamaileon\">Chamaileon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#snacknation\">SnackNation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#yumi\">Yumi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#expat\">Expat.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#dailyharvest\">Daily Harvest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#yumble\">Yumble</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#eof\">Entrepreneurs On Fire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mikelardi\">MikeLardi.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#basepaws\">Basepaws</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#linkedin\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#shark\">Shark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#netflix\">Netflix</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#peloton\">Peloton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#okcupid\">OkCupid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sme\">Social Media Examiner</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#simplehabit\">Simple Habit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#marieforleo\">Marie Forleo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#bulkly\">Bulk.ly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#modsy\">Modsy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#neilstrauss\">Neil Strauss</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#medium\">Medium</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cracku\">Cracku</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Check out these fantastic lead generation form examples and their tactics that you may want to start using on your own forms.</p>\n<h3 id=\"backtotheroots\">1. Back to the Roots</h3>\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-524429\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/messenger-use-in-lead-form-example-back-to-the-roots.jpg\" alt=\"messenger use in lead form example back to the roots\" width=\"1116\" height=\"631\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/messenger-use-in-lead-form-example-back-to-the-roots.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/messenger-use-in-lead-form-example-back-to-the-roots-300x170.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/messenger-use-in-lead-form-example-back-to-the-roots-768x434.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/messenger-use-in-lead-form-example-back-to-the-roots-1024x579.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></h3>\n<p>The Back to the Roots website has some great lead generation form examples, including this very wise use of a chatbot.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Social media type of <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/connect-optinmonster-manychat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ManyChat integration</a> through Facebook Messenger shows the user already &#8220;logged-in&#8221; — giving the sense of trust and reliability</li>\n<li>A <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-create-a-slide-in-scroll-box-optin-form/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">slide-in scroll box optin</a> that doesn&#8217;t disrupt the user experience</li>\n<li>Call to action copy &#8220;Tell me more&#8221; is actionable and written in 1st-person</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"chamaileon\">2. Chamaileon</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-524358\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/distraction-free-landing-page.png\" alt=\"distraction free landing page\" width=\"1116\" height=\"730\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/distraction-free-landing-page.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/distraction-free-landing-page-300x196.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/distraction-free-landing-page-768x502.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/distraction-free-landing-page-1024x670.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>This form from Chamaileon is straight to the point with no distractions and a simple, effective design.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Form submission is more likely with a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-dedicated-form-landing-page-in-wordpress/\">distraction-free landing page</a></li>\n<li>Call to action button uses a bright color and actionable copy</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"snacknation\">3. SnackNation</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524359 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-2-options.png\" alt=\"lead-gen-form-example-with-2-options\" width=\"1116\" height=\"708\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-2-options.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-2-options-300x190.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-2-options-768x487.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-2-options-1024x650.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>SnackNation does an excellent job in this example of using effective <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/yes-no-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">yes/no forms</a> to get visitors to click something and personalize their sales journey themselves.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Personalized questions to identify the type of lead and send them to a page/form based on their needs</li>\n<li>Offers limited options for easier completion, including no &#8220;submit&#8221; button</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"yumi\">4. Yumi</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524360 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-personalization.png\" alt=\"lead-generation-form-example-with-personalization\" width=\"1116\" height=\"726\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-personalization.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-personalization-300x195.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-personalization-768x500.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/example-with-personalization-1024x666.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>This straightforward multi-step form has a contemporary, sleek design to match the brand and help boost conversions, on top of other tactics.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-add-html5-placeholder-text-in-your-wordpress-forms/\">Custom placeholder text</a> in the form fields</li>\n<li>Different stages of the long form are broken down into a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/multi-page-forms/\">multi-page form</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"expat\">5. Expat.com</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524361 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/expat-with-benefits-for-joining.png\" alt=\"expat-with-benefits-for-joining\" width=\"1116\" height=\"760\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/expat-with-benefits-for-joining.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/expat-with-benefits-for-joining-300x204.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/expat-with-benefits-for-joining-768x523.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/expat-with-benefits-for-joining-1024x697.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>What makes Expat.com&#8217;s lead generation form so impressive? The list of bulleted benefits on this split style form helps give visitors the best reasons to convert without taking up too much space.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>List of benefits that lead the eye to a call to action button</li>\n<li>Bright colors for the CTA buttons</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"\">6. Daily Harvest</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524362 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form.jpg\" alt=\"full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"798\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form-300x215.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form-768x549.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/full-page-stunning-visuals-with-multistep-form-1024x732.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>What is a lead generation page and how do you create a lead generation page? Take a look at this Daily Harvest example of a lead generation page with lots of smart conversion tactics, then read our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-dedicated-form-landing-page-in-wordpress/\">how to create a dedicated form landing page in WordPress</a></p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Distraction-free <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/form-pages-addon/\">form page</a></li>\n<li>Stunning hi-res visual</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"yumble\">7. Yumble</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524364 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/geolocation-lead-form-example.jpg\" alt=\"lead form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"556\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/geolocation-lead-form-example.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/geolocation-lead-form-example-300x149.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/geolocation-lead-form-example-768x383.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/geolocation-lead-form-example-1024x510.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Yumble does a great job keeping their lead generation form focused on conversions and the user experience, all at the same time.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A multi-page form for their long form</li>\n<li>Distraction-free full-page design</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"eof\">8. Entrepreneurs On Fire</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524365 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox.jpg\" alt=\"get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox\" width=\"1116\" height=\"661\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox-300x178.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox-768x455.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/get-higher-quality-leads-with-a-confirmation-checkbox-1024x607.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>This confirmation <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-add-a-terms-of-service-checkbox-to-a-form/\">checkbox</a> above the email field is a great tactic to get better conversions.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds a confirmation checkbox to help get higher quality leads by confirming consent in the form instead of in their inbox</li>\n<li>Uses bold colors</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"mikelardi\">9. MikeLardi.com</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524366 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image.png\" alt=\"lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image\" width=\"1116\" height=\"770\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image-300x207.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image-768x530.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-example-with-a-stunning-image-1024x707.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Full-page campaign with a stunning <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-add-a-custom-image-background-for-your-full-page-optin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">custom background visual</a></li>\n<li>Direct call to action copy with the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/700-power-words-that-will-boost-your-conversions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">power word</a> &#8220;freebie&#8221;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"basepaws\">10. Basepaws</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524367 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel.png\" alt=\"lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel\" width=\"1116\" height=\"756\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel-300x203.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel-768x520.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lead-generation-form-example-with-spin-to-win-popup-wheel-1024x694.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Basepaws made sure to include a mention of their Shark Tank appearance right away on their lead generation form, using social proof on top of a few other tactics for getting more conversions.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Exit intent</a> style form triggers as user is exiting the page but before they leave</li>\n<li>Spin-to-win <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/coupon-wheel-optins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">coupon wheel</a> for a fun user experience and high conversions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"linkedin\">11. LinkedIn</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524369 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin-lead-gen-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"605\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/linkedin.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/linkedin-300x163.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/linkedin-768x416.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/linkedin-1024x555.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Most of the content people want to see on LinkedIn is <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/gated-content-marketing-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">gated content</a> that requires you to sign up, so this lead generation form is the first thing many website users see unless they&#8217;re registered.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Distraction-free landing page</li>\n<li>Social media integration for easy registration</li>\n<li>Branded colors create trust in the page since they&#8217;re recognizable</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"shark\">12. Shark</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524370 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/multiple-options-to-sign-up.png\" alt=\"multiple-options-to-sign-up\" width=\"1116\" height=\"679\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/multiple-options-to-sign-up.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/multiple-options-to-sign-up-300x183.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/multiple-options-to-sign-up-768x467.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/multiple-options-to-sign-up-1024x623.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Shark&#8217;s lead generation form example shows how a referral program is a brilliant way to explode your conversions by getting more than one email address per form.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Uses <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/brilliant-examples-of-social-proof-for-your-sites-forms/\">social proof</a> to gather not one but 2 leads at once</li>\n<li>Adds a comment box form field to create the idea the user is sending a personal message to a friend</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"netflix\">13. Netflix</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524371 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/netflix-multipage-form-long-form.jpg\" alt=\"netflix-multipage-form-long-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/netflix-multipage-form-long-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/netflix-multipage-form-long-form-300x168.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/netflix-multipage-form-long-form-768x429.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/netflix-multipage-form-long-form-1024x573.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Netflix&#8217;s lead generation form is straightforward, clean, and distraction-free for maximum conversions.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clear and direct form submission button catches the eye immediately</li>\n<li>Multi-step form to break up a long form</li>\n<li>Actionable copy in the call to action button</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"peloton\">14. Peloton</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524372 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors.jpg\" alt=\"offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors.\" width=\"1116\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors-300x191.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors-768x489.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/offer-a-trial-to-website-visitors-1024x652.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Peloton uses a very popular marketing strategy in this lead generation form — the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/free-to-paid-conversion-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">free trial</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>CTA button is brightly colored and has a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-customize-the-submit-button/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">customized submit button</a> with actionable copy</li>\n<li>Split style template of a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/fullscreen-optin-examples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">full-screen optin</a> with only 3 simple form fields</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"okcupid\">15. OkCupid</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524373 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/okcupid-lead-form.png\" alt=\"okcupid-lead-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"808\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/okcupid-lead-form.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/okcupid-lead-form-300x217.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/okcupid-lead-form-768x556.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/okcupid-lead-form-1024x741.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>OkCupid continues the use of the very popular tactic of distraction-free form pages, on top of some other tricks.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Full-screen landing page to keep potential customers focused</li>\n<li>Strategic psychological use of the color blue to create trust</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"sme\">16. Social Media Examiner</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524374 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/social-proof.jpg\" alt=\"/social-proof.\" width=\"1116\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/social-proof.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/social-proof-300x111.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/social-proof-768x284.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/social-proof-1024x379.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>In this example, Social Media Examiner&#8217;s lead generation form hits a lot of the right tactics to get people to convert into subscribers in exchange for an in-depth report.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Social proof to show how many people have already signed up</li>\n<li>Bold call to action button helps with <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\">email marketing</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Check out this post on our sister site with details on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/how-to-choose-a-perfect-color-scheme-for-your-wordpress-site/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to choose a perfect color scheme for your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"simplehabit\">17. Simple Habit</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524375 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/text-lead.png\" alt=\"/text-lead\" width=\"1116\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/text-lead.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/text-lead-300x113.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/text-lead-768x288.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/text-lead-1024x384.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Because this product is an app, Simple Habit gets right to what they need to do to get their website visitors to convert — download their app.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Only 1 form field asking for phone number on this especially <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/mobile-friendly-popups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mobile-friendly</a> form</li>\n<li>A clear call to action written in 1st person and a colorful button</li>\n<li>Social proof by displaying awards/recognition on the form</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"marieforleo\">18. Marie Forleo</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524376 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2-step-optin-example-with-monsterlinks.png\" alt=\"marie forleo lead generation form example 2 step optin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"723\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2-step-optin-example-with-monsterlinks.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2-step-optin-example-with-monsterlinks-300x194.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2-step-optin-example-with-monsterlinks-768x498.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2-step-optin-example-with-monsterlinks-1024x663.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>To get her visitor&#8217;s email address, this popup lead generation form uses a minimalist design, which matches the overall theme of the entire site.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Asks for just name and email address so the user doesn&#8217;t get overwhelmed</li>\n<li>Offers a strong lead magnet to gain trust with the visitor while also capturing email</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"bulkly\">19. Bulk.ly</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524377 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor.png\" alt=\"actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor\" width=\"1116\" height=\"716\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor-300x192.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor-768x493.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/actionable-call-to-action-form-related-to-visitor-1024x657.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Where do your eyes land when you look at the above image? In this lead generation form example, Bulk.ly made sure that the submit button was the most noticeable part of this popup with bright colors and compelling copy.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Offers an excellent incentive that&#8217;s targeted at their customer&#8217;s needs</li>\n<li>Uses a yes/no button tactic along with a psychological use of color on the button they want users to select</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"modsy\">20. Modsy</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524378 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/breadcrumb-in-multipage-form.jpg\" alt=\"breadcrumb-in-multipage-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"688\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/breadcrumb-in-multipage-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/breadcrumb-in-multipage-form-300x185.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/breadcrumb-in-multipage-form-768x473.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/breadcrumb-in-multipage-form-1024x631.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Modsy knows a smart way to ask for a lot of data and personal information but still get conversions is to break a long form up into steps.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-multi-part-form-in-wordpress/\">Multi-part form</a> displays breadcrumbs to create a better user experience when filling out a long form</li>\n<li>Asks for personal information for a targeted experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"neilstrauss\">21. Neil Strauss</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524379 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/call-to-action-example.png\" alt=\"call-to-action-example\" width=\"1116\" height=\"677\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/call-to-action-example.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/call-to-action-example-300x182.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/call-to-action-example-768x466.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/call-to-action-example-1024x621.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Author and entrepreneur Neil Strauss&#8217; website uses a few tried-and-true lead conversion tactics to promote his email list.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bright call to action button on a fantastic <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/9-lead-magnets-to-increase-subscribers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lead magnet</a></li>\n<li>Displays benefits for signing up and includes power words like &#8220;controversial&#8221; to spark emotion</li>\n<li>Full-screen popup to remove any distractions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"medium\">22. Medium</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-524380 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/cookies-tracking-lead-form.jpg\" alt=\"cookies-tracking-lead-form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"784\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/cookies-tracking-lead-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/cookies-tracking-lead-form-300x211.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/cookies-tracking-lead-form-768x540.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/cookies-tracking-lead-form-1024x719.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Medium very wisely targets visitors based on their browser cookies and display a custom campaign for returning visitors.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Uses <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-target-visitors-based-on-browser-cookies/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">browser cookies</a> as a way to customize the message to returning or new website visitors</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cracku\">23. Cracku</h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-524381\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/countdown-timer-on-form.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1116\" height=\"511\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/countdown-timer-on-form.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/countdown-timer-on-form-300x137.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/countdown-timer-on-form-768x352.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/countdown-timer-on-form-1024x469.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>On top of using a bunch of color psychology, this lead generation form from Cracku creates a sense of urgency to drive conversions and sales.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/countdown-timer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Countdown timers</a> are known to skyrocket form conversion rates</li>\n<li>Call to action button color draws the eye and user to click</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>What Are the Best Lead Generation Tools?</h3>\n<p>There are a lot of high-quality products out there, but only some are the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">best lead generation tools.</a></p>\n<p>Based on ease-of-use and flexibility, <a href=\"http://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a> and <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OptinMonster</a> are our 2 picks.</p>\n<p>They offer easy ways to set up most of the lead generation form tactics in the examples above. On top of that, they integrate with all the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/top-crms-for-your-small-business/\">best CRM</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-email-marketing-service-providers-with-free-options/\">email marketing services</a> so they make it incredibly easy to capture and manage your leads (so you can start making more money online).</p>\n<p>Plus, both products offer a 100% money back guarantee.</p>\n<h3>Final Thoughts</h3>\n<p>And there you have it. Hopefully, these lead generation form examples gave you some great ideas on tactics you can try to increase your own conversion rates.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re really focused on getting your forms to convert better, you may also want to read our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/research-based-tips-to-improve-contact-form-conversions/\">form conversion best practices</a>.</p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for? Get started with the <a href=\"http://wpforms.com\">world&#8217;s best form builder</a> today.</p>\n<p>And don&#8217;t forget to please follow us on <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/lead-generation-forms-examples/\">Lead Generation Forms: 23 Examples That Convert (Like Crazy)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://wpforms.com/lead-generation-forms-examples/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:25:\"https://wpforms.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0